description:
What: Implement channel.create, channel.list, channel.get JSON-RPC handlers in relay/src/ws.rs.

Algorithm (must run AFTER W2B which removes old GROUP_* handlers):
1. Read current relay/src/ws.rs to understand the updated dispatch match structure
2. Add channel handlers:

   rpc_methods::CHANNEL_CREATE => {
     // 1. Parse ChannelCreateParams { guild_cid, path, name, mode }
     // 2. Validate mode is one of: "interactive", "community", "broadcast"
     // 3. Verify caller is guild member: state.inner.store.is_guild_member(&guild_cid, &pub_id).await?
     //    Return error if not member
     // 4. Build ChannelState:
     //    context = AGORA_CONTEXT, type_ = "ChannelState", schema_version = "1"
     //    guild_cid = params.guild_cid, path = params.path, name = params.name
     //    channel_type = "text", mode = params.mode
     //    mls_group_id = if mode != "broadcast" { Some(hex::encode(rand::random::<[u8; 32]>())) } else { None }
     //    channel_secret_b64 = if mode == "broadcast" { Some(base64::encode(rand::random::<[u8; 32]>())) } else { None }
     //    seq = 0, created_at = Utc::now().to_rfc3339(), prev_state_cid = None, proof = None
     //    id = "agora://pending"  // set after signing
     // 5. Sign with relay key: sign_channel_state(&mut state, relay_did, relay_signing_key)?
     // 6. Set state.id = format!("agora://{}/{}", guild_cid, channel_cid)
     // 7. state_json = serde_json::to_string(&state)?
     // 8. Store: state.inner.store.create_channel(&channel_cid, &guild_cid, &path, &name, "text", &mode, mls_group_id.as_deref(), &state_json).await?
     // 9. If mls_group_id is Some, register mapping: state.inner.store.register_mls_group(&mls_group_id, &channel_cid).await?
     // 10. Return ChannelCreateResult { channel_cid, guild_cid, path }
   }

   rpc_methods::CHANNEL_LIST => {
     // 1. Parse ChannelListParams { guild_cid }
     // 2. Verify caller is guild member
     // 3. channel_cids = state.inner.store.list_channels(&guild_cid).await?
     // 4. For each, fetch state_json, parse into ChannelState, build ChannelInfo
     // 5. Return ChannelListResult { channels }
   }

   rpc_methods::CHANNEL_GET => {
     // 1. Parse ChannelGetParams { guild_cid, path }
     // 2. Verify caller is guild member
     // 3. state_json = state.inner.store.get_channel_by_path(&guild_cid, &path).await?
     // 4. Return ChannelGetResult { channel_cid, state_json } or error if not found
   }

Defensive rules:
- Validate mode string: if not one of ["interactive", "community", "broadcast"], return INVALID_PARAMS
- Validate path string: no empty path, no path containing ".." or null bytes
- Validate guild membership before any channel operation
- Random bytes for mls_group_id and channel_secret via rand::random() or OsRng

Run: cargo check -p agora-relay 2>&1
Report: pass/fail, list new handler method names.
